{"tid":1763921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「勿忘初心大遊行」五大訴求 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-11-30T17:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T02:25:23.000Z","uid":202426,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e57335f8d07b980f9e46526f7725db143322088a","tid":1763921,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:03:58.000Z","msg":"繼<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">區選大捷、人權法通過</span></strong>之後，呢一次既遊行十分重要。<br />\n主要原因:<br />\n1.有助大家記得一切行動既<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最終目的</strong></span>係  <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong> <br />\n2. 能夠反映大家對爭取<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可 </span></strong>既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">決心</span></strong><br />\n3. Poly之後，士氣比以前低落，呢一點係無可否認。<br />\n所以，如果今次遊行成功，絕對可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>振奮士氣</strong></span>。<br />\n4. 有助說服<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不同國家</span></strong>加強推動，及實施有關香港的人櫂法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n生於亂世，有一種責任，就係撥亂反正。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n勿忘初心，希望大家可以堅持堅持再堅持，直到黎明來到，成功光復香港。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可  </span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/giPBkEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgiPBkEQ.jpg&h=a319f132&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c64ba522e82df55a1c861b8ddce3ffe4509fd1e3","tid":1763921,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:04:10.000Z","msg":"3點見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b58f7f93854510637dd47a7d35e5a02b78b344","tid":1763921,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.